fern.analysis
Class ShortestPath

java.lang.Object
  fern.analysis.AnalysisBase
      fern.analysis.ShortestPath

public class ShortestPath
extends AnalysisBase

Computes shortest paths in the network by a bfs. Either the path from some source species to only one species can be calculated (by using one of the computePath methods) or paths to all species (by computePaths). A NodeChecker can optionally be given for each method.

Author:
Florian Erhard
